story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA added an event.
message:
OH MY GRILL!!! IT'S WELCOME BACK BBQ!!! 
You call it BRAAI?? Or NYAMA CHOMA?? You tell us!!!
The Point is, it's all gonna be "HOLY SMOKES"!!!

It's MIT, WELLESLEY, and TUFTS Africans getting together to give you your IniMeatAble BBQ. The Lord of the BBQ!!

Featuring the hottest AFROBEATS from all over Africa filled with much fun, energy, passion and lots of laughs.

Good FOOD from your FAVORITE African restaurants and caterers!!! 

VOLLEYBALL, Cornhole, Spikeball, Board games!!!

Oh, and it's FREE. Just bring that hunGRILL stomach to Grill N’ Roll
with us :)

We are very excited to welcome all our MIT Class of 2022 to the start of an exciting four years at MIT, and can’t wait for each of you to create memorable, challenging and successful MIT experiences. You're in!!! Welcome to the  ASA family.❤️
